metadata.name: JuratBTC - Summons to Appear in Court - CHATEX
metadata.description: You have been sued in the United States District Court for the Northern District of Illinois, Case No. 1:23-cv-00779. The Court has entered a Temporary Restraining Order freezing the JTC coins in your account on the JuratBTC blockchain because you have been sanctioned by the United States Treasury Department. Please go to https://jurat.io/notifications to view a copy of the complaint and other important information. You have 21 days to appear in court.
